r"""
MAIL CONVERSATION SUMMARIZER (MSG + PDFs + Images-as-files) — ONE CELL, READY TO PASTE
====================================================================================

Goal
- Read Outlook-exported mail conversations from folders containing .msg
- Also read "loose" PDFs and images that sit in the same folder trees
- Produce ONE summary (<= 2500 words) focusing on:
  - important buyer/supplier questions
  - actual answers/decisions
  - requirements/deadlines/platforms/templates
  - open points
  - ignore greetings/thanks/delegations/scheduling chatter
- Avoid personal data (emails/phones/URLs/IBAN/IDs) in the summary
- Prevent Azure/Nexus "content_filter jailbreak" failures by sanitizing injection-like text

Output files
- DOCX + HTML always
- PDF only if reportlab is installed (otherwise skipped)

Requirements
- openai (AzureOpenAI) configured for GenAI-Nexus
- OPENAI_API_KEY env var already set in notebook session
Optional
- extract-msg  (for .msg parsing)
- pdfplumber or pypdf  (PDF text)
- python-docx (DOCX writing)
- reportlab (PDF writing)

Run
- Paste this entire cell
- Then run: summary_text, stats = run_summary()
"""

